RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT b.customer_no, b.customer_name1, b.short_name FROM oltms_customer b WHERE b.auth_stat = 'A' AND b.record_stat = 'O' ORDER BY 1
SELECT CCY_CODE,CCY_NAME FROM CYTMS_CCY_DEFN ORDER BY CCY_CODE

SELECT a.contract_ref_no FROM oltbs_contract_master a, oltbs_contract b, lbtbs_part_proc_stat c WHERE a.contract_ref_no = b.contract_ref_no AND a.version_no = b.latest_version_no AND c.borrower_ref_no = a.contract_ref_no AND a.tranche_REF_NO = ? AND c.counterparty = ? AND a.module = 'LB' AND a.product_type = 'L' AND b.auth_status = 'A' AND b.contract_status NOT IN ('V', 'H') AND ((a.value_date <= ? AND a.maturity_date >= ?) OR (a.maturity_date <= ? AND b.contract_status = 'A')) AND a.contract_ref_no NOT IN (SELECT drawdown_ref_no FROM TLTBS_FMEM_UPLOAD_DETAIL WHERE contract_ref_no = ? AND event_seq_no = (SELECT MAX(event_seq_no) FROM tltbs_fmem_upload_detail WHERE contract_ref_no = ?))

SELECT a.PRODUCT_CODE, b.product_description FROM LBTBS_BORROWER_DRAWDOWN_PROD a, oltms_product b, OLTMS_PRODUCT_MASTER_LD c, OLVW_AVL_PROD_BR_USR d WHERE a.PRODUCT_CODE = b.product_code AND a.CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND b.product_code = c.product AND c.participant_product IS NOT NULL AND a.product_code = d.product_code AND d.branch_code = global.current_branch AND d.user_id = global.user_id AND a.version_no = (SELECT MAX(version_no) FROM lbtbs_borrower_drawdown_prod WHERE contract_Ref_no = ?) UNION SELECT a.DD_PRODUCT_CODE, b.product_description FROM lbtbs_contract_borr_ddprod a, oltms_product b, OLTMS_PRODUCT_MASTER_LD c, OLVW_AVL_PROD_BR_USR d WHERE a.DD_PRODUCT_CODE = b.product_code AND a.contract_ref_no = ? AND b.product_code = d.product_code AND d.branch_code = global.current_branch AND d.user_id = global.user_id AND a.version_no = (SELECT latest_version_no FROM oltbs_contract WHERE contract_ref_no = ? AND b.product_code = c.product AND c.participant_product IS NOT NULL)

select distinct a.rate_code, a.rate_descr from cftms_rate_code a, cftms_float_rate_master b where a.rate_code = b.rate_code and a.record_stat = 'O' and a.auth_stat = 'A' and b.ccy_code = ? and a.branch_code = global.current_branch and a.branch_code = b.branch_code union select rate_code,rate_code_desc from lftms_standard_rate_code where rate_type='S'and record_stat='O'and auth_stat='A' UNION SELECT DISTINCT RATE_CODE, RATE_DESCR FROM CFTMS_RFR_MASTER WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND TYPE = NVL(?,TYPE) ORDER BY RATE_CODE
select rate_code,rate_code_desc from lftms_standard_rate_code where rate_type='S'and record_stat='O'and auth_stat='A'

select distinct ccy, CCY_NAME from LBTBS_BORROWER_CCY a, CYTMS_CCY_DEFN b WHERE a.ccy = b.ccy_code AND a.CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND a.version_no = (select max(version_no) from LBTBS_BORROWER_CCY WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = ?)

SELECT A.CUSTOMER_NO, b.short_name, b.gfcid FROM LBTBS_CONTRACT_BORROWERS A, oltms_customer b, OLTBS_CONTRACT c where A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? and a.customer_no = b.customer_no and b.auth_stat = 'A' and b.record_stat = 'O' and a.contract_ref_no = c.contract_ref_no and a.Version_no = c.Latest_version_no and nvl(a.blocked,'N') = 'N' and c.CONTRACT_STATUS IN ('Y','A') order by a.customer_no

SELECT a.Contract_Ref_No FROM Oltbs_Contract a, Lbtbs_Contract_Borrowers b, Oltbs_Contract_Master c WHERE b.Contract_Ref_No = a.Contract_Ref_No AND b.Version_No = a.Latest_Version_No AND c.Contract_Ref_No = a.Contract_Ref_No AND c.Version_No = a.Latest_Version_No AND c.Cusip_No = ? AND Nvl(c.Agency_Type, 'L') = 'P' AND c.Product_Type = 'C' AND a.Contract_Status = 'A' AND b.Customer_No = a.Counterparty AND a.Module_Code = 'LB' AND ? = 'M' AND ? = 'Y' AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM Lbtbs_Tranche_Vdbal_Master e WHERE e.Contract_Ref_No = a.Contract_Ref_No AND e.Balance_Type = 'TRANSFER_AVL' AND e.Value_Date <= TO_DATE(?, 'YY-MON-DD') AND e.Value_Date = (SELECT MAX(f.Value_Date) FROM Lbtb_Tranche_Vdbal_Master f WHERE f.Contract_Ref_No = e.Contract_Ref_No AND f.Balance_Type = 'TRANSFER_AVL' AND f.Value_Date <= TO_DATE(?, 'YY-MON-DD'))) AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM Lbtbs_Agency_Wrapper_Browser WHERE Wrapper_Ref_No = a.Contract_Ref_No)

select distinct DRAWDOWN_REF_NO from tltb_fmem_upload_detail a WHERE contract_ref_no in (select contract_ref_no from tltbs_contract_master where trade_date = ? and currency = ? and cusip_no = ? and position_identifier = ? and buy_sell = 'B') and event_seq_no = (select max(event_seq_no) from tltb_fmem_upload_detail where contract_ref_no = a.contract_ref_no) and contract_ref_no not in (select contract_ref_no from TLTBS_SETTLEMENT_MASTER where contract_ref_no = a.contract_ref_no and NVL(settle_status, '@') = 'Y' and event_seq_no = (select max(event_seq_no) from TLTBS_SETTLEMENT_MASTER where contract_ref_no = a.contract_ref_no)) AND a.contract_ref_no <> ? and a.drawdown_ref_no not in (select drawdown_ref_no from tltb_fmem_upload_detail where contract_ref_no = ?)
SELECT LOV, LOV_DESC FROM OLTM_USER_FIELDS_LOV WHERE FUNCTION_ID ='LBDDDONL' AND FIELD_NAME ='RATEBASIS'
SELECT A.COMPONENT,A.COMPONENT_DESCRIPTION FROM LFTMS_PRODUCT_ICCF A WHERE A.PRODUCT = ? AND NVL(A.STOP_APPLICATION, 'N') = 'N' ORDER BY NVL(A.UNFUND_COMPONENT, 'N')
